<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-6452] @Grab group element is documented as optional but the implementation requires it</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-6452</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The javadoc for &lt;tt&gt;@Grab&lt;/tt&gt; lists &lt;tt&gt;group&lt;/tt&gt; as an optional element. However, it is no more optional than &lt;tt&gt;module&lt;/tt&gt; or &lt;tt&gt;version&lt;/tt&gt; (which are both listed as required).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12817219">GROOVY-6452</key>
            <summary>@Grab group element is documented as optional but the implementation requires it</summary>
